OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry and clear with some patchy
OL,9,Ffog and low cloud. Turning cloudier in
OL,10,Fthe southwest with a few showers later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMainly dry and bright with
OL,13,Fjust the odd shower. Outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fwill spread northeast during late
OL,15,Fafternoon and evening. Warm,
OL,16,Fespecially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
